                    </div>
                    <div class="bayesian-step">
                        <strong>Evidence:</strong> Huang et al. (2025) meta-analysis (22 studies)<br>
                        Dose-response relationship confirmed, but observational only<br>
                        ‚Üí Posterior: 0.60 ‚Üí 0.65 (BF = 1.5, weak evidence)
                    </div>
